Nvidia Earnings
---------------

From the Wall Street Journal ( https://www.wsj.com/business/earnings/nvidia=
-earnings-q3-2024-nvda-stock-08f3337d ) :

Nvidia=E2=80=99s sales surged in its latest quarter and profits more than d=
oubled, a sign of the strength of an artificial-intelligence boom that has =
made the company the world=E2=80=99s most valuable. Nvidia on Wednesday als=
o projected around $37.5 billion of revenue for its current quarter, toppin=
g forecasts and suggesting its next-generation AI chips, known as Blackwell=
, are in high demand from customers like Microsoft, Google, Meta and Elon M=
usk=E2=80=99s xAI. The company, whose chips have powered the rise of AI tec=
hnology, said it expects the Blackwell chips to ship in the current quarter=
 and be in short supply into its next fiscal year. Sales were $35.1 billion=
 in the fiscal third quarter, the company said, up 94% from a year prior an=
d ahead of forecasts in a FactSet survey of analysts. Profit reached $19.3 =
billion, also ahead of Wall Street forecasts.

